name: 025 Pie
description:
" Sometimes our memories...
Some pictures from the past, some scenes
A pie. 
Sometimes I get throught my memories and I find dumb shit, useless facts, moments. Things
A pie, that I eat.
A long shot.
Hard to swallow pie,
To understand the life, I'm living.
Hard to swallow pie,
That takes me a long time to eat,
Hard to throw out...
And a long shot, 
Frozen as a memory that won't ever leave me,
As a ghost following me,
As a strenght I gained, feeling my

 life. "

Ambers of The Realtime [19-27] : The Ghost series
